instructions: put the plate at the center of the charger
Put the napkin at the center of the plate
Put the dinner fork on the left side of the charger
put the salad fork by the left side of the dinner fork
put the dinner knife on the right side of the charger
put the tea spoon on the right side of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon at the right side of the tea spoon
put the water glass above the dinner knife
put the wine glass by the right side of the water glass
put another wine glass in between the first wine glass and tea spoon
put a coffee cup by the right side of the second wine glass
put the bread plate above the two forks
put a butter knife horizontally at the center of the bread plate
put a dessert fork horizontally in between bread plate and water glass
put a dessert spoon between dessert fork and charger horizontally, pointing at bread plate<br>
